# Error Reporting - AI & Human Readable

## Core Requirement
Send all errors to readable place for AI & human

## Implementation

### Error Panel (top-right)
```css
.error-panel { position: fixed; top: 10px; right: 10px; z-index: 10000; }
```

### JavaScript Error Handler
```javascript
window.errorReporter = new ErrorReporter();
window.reportError = (type, message, source) => { /* manual reporting */ };
```

